      "value": "<h3><strong>WARNING: This entry contains spoilers for the Dead Sun Adventure Path.</strong></h3>\n<p>This unique weapon belonged to a Knight of Golarion who attempted to kill Serovox a few years before the signing of the Absalom Pact and the creation of the Corpse Fleet. It is a golden spear with a ruby blade and functions as both an inferno flame doshko and a white star plasma caster. It holds one ultra-capacity battery, which powers all uses of the weapon. Switching the weapon from melee functionality to ranged functionality (or vice versa) is a swift action.</p>"
